WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.933 --> 00:00:03.000
If I get caught,

2
00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.100
do you think you can escape?

3
00:00:05.366 --> 00:00:07.300
I was just joking with you.

4
00:00:07.466 --> 00:00:08.700
Don’t worry.

5
00:00:08.700 --> 00:00:10.166
When Consort Rong is punished,

6
00:00:10.333 --> 00:00:12.233
the scene will definitely be chaotic.

7
00:00:12.366 --> 00:00:12.933
At that time,

8
00:00:12.933 --> 00:00:16.166
I will have my people meet you at the East Gate.

9
00:00:16.266 --> 00:00:18.466
What grudge or enmity do you have with Su Qingyu?

10
00:00:18.666 --> 00:00:19.900
No grudge, no enmity.

11
00:00:20.133 --> 00:00:22.300
But he loves me and wants me to be the Empress.

12
00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:23.100
Hmph.

13
00:00:23.366 --> 00:00:26.866
If the problem can’t be solved, eliminate the person who created it.

14
00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:28.766
As long as Su Qingyu is alive,

15
00:00:28.966 --> 00:00:31.466
even if the Empress Dowager makes me the Empress,

16
00:00:31.666 --> 00:00:33.666
the Emperor will never agree.

17
00:00:34.533 --> 00:00:36.266
Even if Su Qingyu dies,

18
00:00:36.266 --> 00:00:38.200
you still cannot be the Empress.

19
00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:40.366
The Empress Dowager will never let you be the Empress

20
00:00:40.366 --> 00:00:42.566
for the sake of her own family.

21
00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:45.033
You don’t need to worry about that.

22
00:00:45.266 --> 00:00:46.900
Once Su Qingyu is dead,

23
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:49.300
the Empress Dowager will naturally obey me.

24
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:50.933
And I’ll become the Empress.

25
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:52.666
However, for the Emperor,

26
00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:54.666
as long as Su Qingyu is gone,

27
00:00:54.666 --> 00:00:57.066
it doesn’t matter who becomes the Empress.

28
00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:58.766
Hahahaha.

29
00:01:06.300 --> 00:01:08.100
Empress Dowager, long life and peace.

30
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:09.900
If it weren’t for your care,

31
00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:12.100
I wouldn’t be feeling unwell today.

32
00:01:12.500 --> 00:01:14.600
I can only stay in bed.

33
00:01:14.666 --> 00:01:17.000
Do you need me to help you with a back rub?

34
00:01:17.266 --> 00:01:21.233
No need. Just go get me a cup of tea.

35
00:01:25.500 --> 00:01:28.100
The secret medicine I prepared this time,

36
00:01:28.366 --> 00:01:31.000
as long as you put the phlegm in the tea,

37
00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.966
and let the Empress Dowager drink it,

38
00:01:33.166 --> 00:01:35.466
she will follow your commands.

39
00:01:35.666 --> 00:01:37.766
She will obey you.

40
00:01:48.733 --> 00:01:50.366
Leave it to Wang Momo.

41
00:01:50.366 --> 00:01:53.600
So that the Empress Dowager won’t pass the illness on to you.

42
00:02:06.966 --> 00:02:09.166
Leave it to Wang Momo.

43
00:02:10.266 --> 00:02:11.900
Thank you, Consort De.
